### Create System User
POST {{BASE_URL}}/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "nome": "Admin Sistema",
  "email": "admin@hospital.com",
  "senha": "admin123",
  "roles": ["ADMIN", "USUARIO"],
  "unidadeId": 1,
  "profissionalId": null,
  "pacienteId": null
}

### Get All Users
GET {{BASE_URL}}/usuarios
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get User by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/usuarios/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Update User
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/usuarios/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "nome": "Admin Sistema Principal",
  "email": "admin@hospital.com",
  "roles": ["ADMIN", "USUARIO", "SUPER_ADMIN"],
  "unidadeId": 1,
  "ativo": true
}

### Deactivate User
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/usuarios/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}